    <h1>Discover Serbia</h1>
    <p>Serbia offers opportunities for cultural tourism in cities like Belgrade and Niš, outdoor adventures like hiking and rafting in its natural landscapes, and relaxation in thermal spas and historic wine regions.</p>
    <h2>Packages</h2>
    <p>We offer an extensive range of holiday solutions to accommodate the needs of all our clients. From daily excursions in the most beautiful cities, to thorough tours of hidden villages and mountains and ortodox monastery to discover Serbia's lesser-known sides.</p>
